14:50.623 --> 14:51.290
DISPLACED RESIDENTS IN TOXIC

14:51.290 --> 14:52.759
TRAILERS.

14:52.759 --> 14:53.793
UNIVERSITY OF DELAWARE PROFESSOR

14:53.793 --> 14:55.561
RICK SYLVES STUDIES FEMA AND

14:55.561 --> 14:56.562
JOINS ME NOW TO DISCUSS ITS

14:56.562 --> 14:58.030
CHANGES DURING THE PAST DECADE.

14:58.030 --> 14:58.798
I THINK THE QUESTION MOST PEOPLE

14:58.798 --> 15:00.366
ARE GOING TO WONDER IS HAS FEMA

15:00.366 --> 15:01.100
IMPROVED?

15:01.100 --> 15:02.101
AND IF SO, HOW?

15:02.101 --> 15:04.203
>> YES, THEY DO EXTREMELY GOOD

15:04.203 --> 15:07.173
JOBS ON RELATIVELY SMALL-SCALE

15:07.173 --> 15:07.840
DISASTERS.

15:07.840 --> 15:10.476
THEY'VE DONE A TREMENDOUSLY GOOD

15:10.476 --> 15:12.845
JOB IN ENHANCING THE CAPACITY OF

15:12.845 --> 15:14.747
STATE AND LOCAL GOVERNMENT

15:14.747 --> 15:15.414
EMERGENCY MANAGEMENT.

15:15.414 --> 15:17.016
IF ANYTHING, THE FIELD OF

15:17.016 --> 15:19.352
EMERGENCY MANAGEMENT THAT'S

15:19.352 --> 15:21.020
GROWING EVEN ACADEMICALLY ACROSS

15:21.020 --> 15:23.389
THE COUNTRY OWES ITS ORIGINS TO

15:23.389 --> 15:25.158
FEMA, AND WE NEED TO THANK THAT

15:25.158 --> 15:26.626
AGENCY FOR THAT.

15:26.626 --> 15:28.661
IN ADDITION, FEW OTHER COUNTRIES

15:28.661 --> 15:30.763
HAVE FEMA-LIKE EMERGENCY

15:30.763 --> 15:32.632
MANAGEMENT ORGANIZATIONS.

15:32.632 --> 15:35.168
EVEN THE MOST DEVELOPED DON'T

15:35.168 --> 15:37.370
COME CLOSE TO PROVIDING, THROUGH

15:37.370 --> 15:41.140
AGENCIES LIKE FEMA, THE RANGE OF

15:41.140 --> 15:42.008
POST-DISASTER ASSISTANCE THAT

15:42.008 --> 15:43.209
THIS COUNTRY PROVIDES.

15:43.209 --> 15:43.876
>> Sreenivasan: AT THE SAME

15:43.876 --> 15:45.044
TIME, THIS IS STILL HOUSED

15:45.044 --> 15:45.645
INSIDE THE DEPARTMENT OF

15:45.645 --> 15:46.746
HOMELAND SECURITY?

15:46.746 --> 15:47.480
>> YES.

15:47.480 --> 15:50.650
I THINK THIS HAS BEEN A

15:50.650 --> 15:52.084
PREDICAMENT EVER SINCE THAT--

15:52.084 --> 15:54.053
EVER SINCE IT WAS FOLDED INTO

15:54.053 --> 15:55.755
DEPARTMENT OF HOMELAND SECURITY

15:55.755 --> 15:57.023
IN 2002.

15:57.023 --> 15:59.125
ONE OF THE PROBLEMS IS THAT

15:59.125 --> 16:00.860
HOMELAND SECURITY'S MISSION IS

16:00.860 --> 16:03.196
TO COUNTER TERRORISM.

16:03.196 --> 16:07.466
AND FEMA'S JOB IS TO PROVIDE,

16:07.466 --> 16:10.837
REALLY, DISASTER ASSISTANCE AND

16:10.837 --> 16:11.704
PROVIDE FOR PREPARE

16:11.704 --> 16:13.039
UNDERSTANDNESS FOR DISASTERS.

16:13.039 --> 16:14.473
AND CLEARLY THERE ARE TERRORISM

16:14.473 --> 16:17.476
DUTIES THAT LEGITIMATELY FALL TO

16:17.476 --> 16:17.810
FEMA.

16:17.810 --> 16:19.011
BUT, UNFORTUNATELY, WHEN THEY

16:19.011 --> 16:21.948
TAKE ON THESE DUTIES, THEY ALSO

16:21.948 --> 16:23.249
HAVE-- THEY TAKE ON REQUIREMENTS

16:23.249 --> 16:25.184
OF STATE SECRECY THAT MAKE THE

16:25.184 --> 16:27.720
AGENCY MUCH LESS TRANSPARENT

16:27.720 --> 16:29.155
THAN IT PROBABLY SHOULD BE,

16:29.155 --> 16:30.957
PARTICULARLY GIVEN ITS CIVILIAN

16:30.957 --> 16:32.992
RESPONSIBILITIES AND DISASTER

16:32.992 --> 16:33.559
CIRCUMSTANCES.

