>> THE MONEY HAS INCREASED

16:46.505 --> 16:47.173
SIGNIFICANTLY.

16:47.173 --> 16:48.708
THERE IS A PRESIDENT'S DISASTER

16:48.708 --> 16:50.710
FUND THAT IS THE MAIN RECEPTACLE

16:50.710 --> 16:52.545
FOR MONIES TO BE DISPENSED NOT

16:52.545 --> 16:54.814
ONLY TO FEMA BUT TO A GREAT MANY

16:54.814 --> 16:55.915
OTHER FEDERAL AGENCIES THAT ARE

16:55.915 --> 16:57.483
CALLED INTO ACTION DURING

16:57.483 --> 16:59.252
PERIODS OF DISASTER.

